    "headline": "Henry Schein (NASDAQ:HSIC) Beats Q1 CY2026 Sales Expectations",
    "summary": "Dental and medical products company Henry Schein (NASDAQ:HSIC) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 6.3% year on year to $3.37 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.32 per share was 8.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
